  "body": "In master (and v0.6.0), OSD pods fail to start with the following message when running on Kuberenets 1.6.4 or lower:\r\n```\r\n$ kubectl -n rook get pod\r\nNAME                              READY     STATUS                                         RESTARTS   AGE\r\nrook-api-3536545610-54f3w         1/1       Running                                        0          23s\r\nrook-ceph-mgr0-1387429650-b9xj6   1/1       Running                                        0          24s\r\nrook-ceph-mgr1-2636939030-rmwws   1/1       Running                                        0          23s\r\nrook-ceph-mon0-rwx00              1/1       Running                                        0          55s\r\nrook-ceph-mon1-pfg7r              1/1       Running                                        0          44s\r\nrook-ceph-mon2-h4d1w              1/1       Running                                        0          36s\r\nrook-ceph-osd-32bkx               0/1       container's runAsUser breaks non-root policy   0          23s\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is a regression associated with #1188\r\n\r\nThis appears to be the upstream Kuberentes issue: https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/46996",
